<p>Hi there! I'm <strong>Ngọc Thái Thị Bảo</strong>, the person behind I'm Pumpkin.</p>

<p>I started this blog to share my travel stories, the little moments that make me smile, and the beautiful corners of the world that take my breath away. Whether it's getting lost in the streets of Tokyo, touching the walls of the Taj Mahal, or tasting street food in Bangkok — I believe every journey has a story worth telling.</p>

<p>When I'm not traveling, you can find me planning my next adventure, editing photos, or dreaming about my next bowl of phở.</p>

<p>Thank you for being here. I hope my stories inspire you to explore, to wonder, and most importantly — to smile.</p>

